{"tid":179301,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"被仆街同事串，點算好>?","createTime":"2017-03-30T07:02:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-30T09:59:43.000Z","uid":69603,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"912645c96f3862c1fa8a7660b57f86adac48a8a1","tid":179301,"uid":69603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T07:02:14.000Z","msg":"小弟做緊戈間公司，有條仆街女同事，人醜矮肥，我就唔提啦(圖同老母都無) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n重點係，成日做錯野，人地提番佢，佢就會用一把好撚想煎尻佢番面的表情同語氣同你講. 你好叻呀. 點解你可以咁叻既?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如題，你係被串的同事. 各巴打會點回佢"},{"pid":"7a2b630f60f3737c0fd12245a90a4c4f9e500937","tid":179301,"uid":68805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T07:03:35.000Z","msg":"唔撚理佢,盡量各做各,唔同好同佢撞file,收工求神早日收佢皮"},{"pid":"a80b57986e998ae6ff49bec8c2328526fe855c16","tid":179301,"uid":64576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T07:04:20.000Z","msg":"戈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n抵你畀人串啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1ec429f11b0e391a2f714129610a2e4f8de8d43","tid":179301,"uid":69603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T07:05:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>戈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n抵你畀人串啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n難道你要小弟打那間公司嗎?"},{"pid":"6259877b2ddac84ceca51cf2669895365c159081","tid":179301,"uid":57555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T07:05:49.000Z","msg":"唔係我叻，係你蠢<br />\n檢討下點解成日有位比人入"},{"pid":"51df13fa9a3120756b337a0a5cafdbebc9d76010","tid":179301,"uid":69603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0